Heislerville's population as of 2020 was 227,<ref name=Census2020/> while the 2010 census showed a count of 451.{{Citation needed|date=June 2023}} There are approximately 200 housing units in its approximate nine-mile radius of which {{convert|8.17|sqmi}} is land and {{convert|0.02|sqmi}} is water.

